Depending on version of prestashop please apply the patch.

To apply patch. go to your prestashop directory and execute :

patch -i <patch_file_name>

=========================
prestashop_v148.patch
==========================

patch for prestashop version 1.4.8
Enable and Add Web services for TAX RULES and TAX RULES GROUP.

=========================
prestashop_v147.patch
==========================

patch for prestashop version 1.4.7
Enable and Add Web services for TAX RULES and TAX RULES GROUP.

==========================
prestashop_tax_api.patch
==========================

patch for prestashop version 1.4
Fix Web services for TAX
Enable and Add Web services for TAX, TAX RULES and TAX RULES GROUP.
